cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT. 

The paper deals with optimization of content caching in wireless small cell networks, which is a problem related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a clustering algorithm and a reinforcement learning algorithm, which are related to artificial intelligence and machine learning, respectively. Hence, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper involves optimization of caching strategy, which is related to information theory and optimization, making cs.IT (Information Theory) a possible category as well.
